173
00:08:38,340 --> 00:08:43,180
♪I'm afraid we can't change our fate in this life♪

174
00:08:44,500 --> 00:08:47,340
♪I do not fear. I do not hide♪

175
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:50,820
♪I can no longer bear the pain♪

176
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:58,020
♪It grows as time passes♪

177
00:08:58,620 --> 00:09:00,260
♪Time will not tell you♪

178
00:09:00,700 --> 00:09:02,300
♪That I have been missing you♪

179
00:09:02,620 --> 00:09:05,060
♪You are all I think about♪

180
00:09:05,700 --> 00:09:07,020
♪No matter♪

181
00:09:07,180 --> 00:09:08,460
♪How harshly♪

182
00:09:08,460 --> 00:09:12,140
♪Life treats me♪

183
00:09:12,780 --> 00:09:14,180
♪I can only let go of my hate♪

184
